{"tid":1969270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"縱橫遊：取消所有旅行團至6．19","createTime":"2020-04-12T09:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T14:06:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c414328bdfba6a29a483a121b30ab9b253457ad","tid":1969270,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"【17:55】政府對由內地抵港者實施強制檢疫令，有效期至5月7日，旅行社縱橫遊昨（11日）宣布，首個內地團將於5月9日出發。縱橫遊今午（12日）5時許在facebook表示，因應衛生署呼籲5月不建議外遊，決定將所有旅行團取消至6月19日。<br />\n<br />\n【15:03】縱橫遊今日（12日）表示，此前取消所有內地旅行團至5月7日，會繼續根據港府的回港隔離措施及新型冠狀病毒疫情情況，稍後決定會否將取消旅行團的日期延長。<br />\n<br />\n縱橫遊指出，由5月8日起至今年夏季，甚至秋季的內地旅行團，一直以來都是開放報名，只是因應港府措施而未有取消，強調一直以旅客的安全為先，呼籲政府加快決定從內地回港的隔離措施會否取消及延長，以讓業界可一致行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200412/s00001/1586673423677/%e7%b8%b1%e6%a9%ab%e9%81%8a-%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c%e5%9c%98%e8%87%b36-19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200412%2Fs00001%2F1586673423677%2F%25e7%25b8%25b1%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%2581%258a-%25e5%258f%2596%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%2589%2580%25e6%259c%2589%25e6%2597%2585%25e8%25a1%258c%25e5%259c%2598%25e8%2587%25b36-19&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=221ca00c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200412%2Fs00001%2F1586673423677%2F%25e7%25b8%25b1%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%2581%258a-%25e5%258f%2596%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%2589%2580%25e6%259c%2589%25e6%2597%2585%25e8%25a1%258c%25e5%259c%2598%25e8%2587%25b36-19&h=54a531fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200412/s00001/1586673423677/%e7%b8%b1%e6%a9%ab%e9%81%8a-%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c%e5%9c%98%e8%87%b36-19</a>"},{"pid":"434c98eb6665c5a8da0c9d8a40c58aff3edaae80","tid":1969270,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"